# Note: */analysis/ folders under src/ are intentionally NOT listed here.
# They hold personal, manual exploration and are versioned like the rest
# of src/ — see docs/CONVENTIONS.md, "Analysis folders" section.

# Byte-compiled / optimized / DLL files
__pycache__/
*.py[codz]
*$py.class


